11#import <Foundation/Foundation.h>
12
13#import "RTCMacros.h"
14
15NS_ASSUME_NONNULL_BEGIN
16
17/** Corresponds to webrtc::Priority. */
18typedef NS_ENUM(NSInteger, RTCPriority) {
19 RTCPriorityVeryLow,
20 RTCPriorityLow,
21 RTCPriorityMedium,
22 RTCPriorityHigh
23};
24
25RTC_OBJC_EXPORT
26__attribute__((objc_runtime_name("WK_RTCRtpEncodingParameters")))
27@interface RTCRtpEncodingParameters : NSObject
28
29/** The idenfifier for the encoding layer. This is used in simulcast. */
30@property(nonatomic, copy, nullable) NSString *rid;
31
32/** Controls whether the encoding is currently transmitted. */
33@property(nonatomic, assign) BOOL isActive;
34
35/** The maximum bitrate to use for the encoding, or nil if there is no
36 * limit.
37 */
38@property(nonatomic, copy, nullable) NSNumber *maxBitrateBps;
39
40/** The minimum bitrate to use for the encoding, or nil if there is no
41 * limit.
42 */
43@property(nonatomic, copy, nullable) NSNumber *minBitrateBps;
44
45/** The maximum framerate to use for the encoding, or nil if there is no
46 * limit.
47 */
48@property(nonatomic, copy, nullable) NSNumber *maxFramerate;
49
50/** The requested number of temporal layers to use for the encoding, or nil
51 * if the default should be used.
52 */
53@property(nonatomic, copy, nullable) NSNumber *numTemporalLayers;
54
55/** Scale the width and height down by this factor for video. If nil,
56 * implementation default scaling factor will be used.
57 */
58@property(nonatomic, copy, nullable) NSNumber *scaleResolutionDownBy;
59
60/** The SSRC being used by this encoding. */
61@property(nonatomic, readonly, nullable) NSNumber *ssrc;
62
63/** The relative DiffServ Code Point priority. */
64@property(nonatomic, assign) RTCPriority networkPriority;
65
66- (instancetype)init NS_DESIGNATED_INITIALIZER;
67
68@end
69
70NS_ASSUME_NONNULL_END
71
